---
title: Mumbai Eggplant Curry & Garlic Rice with Veggies, Peanuts & Yoghurt
description: This vibrant eggplant curry has flavour bursting in every bite! The garlic rice is fluffy and packed with savoury goodness, balanced against the roast veggies and Mumbai-style spices, we reckon it’s a sure winner at the dinner table.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
